{
  "stem": "812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have five beautiful grandchildren-- Arielle and Joshua, Gavi, Dalia, and Yo'av.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Michael and Rachel and the family are now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, too, again, are mixed feelings with that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we miss them terribly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We love them dearly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they gave up much here-- material things, only material things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we're very, very, very proud of them that they took it upon themselves to-- to fulfill their inner feelings and-- and hope and to live and-- to give up all that they gave up here to live and fulfill their dream in Israel.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there is no doubt that if we had an Israel at that time, many, many more of us would have survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was not a place in this whole world that would take us in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if we had an Israel then, it would have been altogether different.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were on this truck, and we first stopped in Leipzig, I remember, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had various stops, actually, before we arrived in Holland, obviously, too, because you couldn't do that all in one stretch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Leipzig, I remember we were sitting at a-- oh, a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a long table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We must have been in-- in some hotel type of a place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not a hotel-- where soldiers are taken care of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a long table, and it was summertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was June.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were all given beer, and I remember enjoying that glass of beer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was in-- in Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we headed on towards Maastricht, which was in Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there we were put up in a cloister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother had a terrible toothache.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
